dy aspects of interacting Fermi liquids, which are often thought to be\nwell understood theoretically, remaining unexplored.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 18:00:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 15:52:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-23"}
