que opportunity to measure companion\noutflow velocity, predict regions of weak and strong lensing, and in principle\nindependently constrain orbital inclinations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 20:26:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Aug 2022 19:00:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2022 06:14:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
