lytic profiles. We also tested our implementation of\ndust using two formalisms: an analytic prescription for the opacity devised by\nBowen and the full treatment of carbon-dust formation. Both simulations\nreproduce the 1D analytic solution displaying the expected additional\nacceleration when the gas temperature falls below the condensation temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2022 20:29:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
