eference (FR) PCQA methods. The ablation studies\nfurther verify the rationality of the proposed framework and confirm the\ncontributions made by the quality-aware features extracted via the dynamic\nviewing manner.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 08:59:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 11 Sep 2022 05:48:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-13"}
