e of 64% improvement in the thermal enhancement factor is\nachieved using LES for a B/H ratio of 0.75. Two correlations are proposed to\ncalculate the friction factor and thermal enhancement factor for a given Re, Nu\nand (B/H) ratio, with a R-squared value of 0.94 and 0.96 respectively based on\nthe obtained simulated results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 09:38:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-01"}
